# ArticleReferences

A card component for displaying reference links related to an article, with icons for different document types.

## Import

```typescript
import { ArticleReferences } from '@happyvertical/svelte';
```

## Basic Usage

<div class="example">
  <div class="example-preview" style="width: 100%; max-width: 500px;">
    <ArticleReferences references={sampleReferences} />
  </div>
</div>

```svelte
<script>
  const references = [
    {
      title: 'Council Meeting Agenda',
      url: '/docs/agenda.pdf',
      type: 'agenda',
      description: 'January 15, 2024 Meeting'
    },
    {
      title: 'Meeting Minutes',
      url: '/docs/minutes.pdf',
      type: 'minutes'
    }
  ];
</script>

<ArticleReferences {references} />
```

## Custom Title

<div class="example">
  <div class="example-preview" style="width: 100%; max-width: 500px;">
    <ArticleReferences references={sampleReferences.slice(0, 2)} title="Source Documents" />
  </div>
</div>

```svelte
<ArticleReferences {references} title="Source Documents" />
```

